      "raw_url": "https://github.com/tenzir/tenzir/raw/731b61aa8c9cefa78ebeac1e664f939966c0583e/changelog%2Freleases%2Fv5.11.1%2Fmanifest.yaml",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/tenzir/tenzir/contents/changelog%2Freleases%2Fv5.11.1%2Fmanifest.yaml?ref=731b61aa8c9cefa78ebeac1e664f939966c0583e",
      "patch": "@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@\n created: 2025-08-01\n title: \"HTTP Fix and Compression for Azure Log Analytics\"\n-intro: |\n+intro: >-\n   This release introduces payload compression for Azure Log Analytics to reduce bandwidth usage, as well as an important fix for a `from_http` bug that was introduced with the previous release."
