      "patch": "@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@\n created: 2025-09-11\n title: \"SentinelOne Data Lake\"\n-intro: |\n+intro: >-\n   This release introduces an integration fo SentinelOne Singularity\u2122 Data Lake and a new message based `to_kafka` operator that features a one to one event to message relation."
    },
