      "patch": "@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@\n created: 2025-11-03\n title: \"Better Memory Allocation\"\n-intro: |\n+intro: >-\n   We continue our quest for better memory usage by switching out the memory allocator to the battle-tested `mimalloc`, as well as adding metrics collecting for memory usage."
    },
